data.description: Discover your dream oasis! This spacious 3-bedroom, 2-bath pool home boasts a thoughtfully designed split bedroom floor plan. The large kitchen is a culinary delight with abundant cabinets, a center island, and luxurious marble countertops. The expansive master bedroom features 2 closets, one being a walk-in, and sliders leading to the inviting pool. The en suite bath offers a double vanity and a walk-in shower. The 3rd bedroom doubles as a cozy den with a wood-burning fireplace and a convenient wet bar. The current owner is a master woodworker and has many custom built features. Enjoy the utmost privacy in this serene 1/3-acre property, complete with four flourishing fruit trees and expansive views. Your perfect retreat awaits!
